<L>__{exterior "guardian angel" theater day}
<D>__{peppy miller is "the guardian angel". it's a huge poster on the facade of a movie theater. george goes inside. with jack.}
<L>__{interior "guardian angel" theater day}
<D>__{the auditorium is full. george sits down in the first row. to watch the film he has to look upwards, and sees a huge and magnificent peppy rising above him. she's playing a scene with a young actor we recognize, it's humphrey bogart. he's become a spectator: he laughs, is absorbed and cries along with the others.}
